            <title>[LOG4J2-2476] org.apache.log4j.SimpleLayout and ConsoleAppender missing in log4j-1.2-api</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/LOG4J2-2476</link>
                <project id="12310790" key="LOG4J2">Log4j 2</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve tried to update log4j from 1.2.17 to 2.11.1.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This seems to work for a lot of libraries but not for that ones that are configuring log4j programmatically&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example crystal reports seems to use log4j 1.2 and its SimpleLayout.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;So if I try to update log4j to the latest version I get a NoClassdefFoundError.&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;ConsoleAppender seems to be missing too?&#160;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Could you please readd this classes to log4j-1.2-api?&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
